TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN

1. In Telegram, find the official bot @BotFather.

2. Send "/newbot" and choose a bot name and username (the username must end with "bot").

3. BotFather will send you a token that looks like:
   
   "123456789:AAExxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
   
   This is your "TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN".

4. If you already have a bot, you can regenerate the token using the "/token" command in BotFather. The old token will stop working immediately.

